column2: SELECT m.name as cscname, m.obsid, d.dr7objid, d.dr8objid, n.objid as dr1#objid, m.ra AS ra_csc, m.dec AS dec_csc, m.err_ellipse_r0, m.err_ellipse_r1, m.err_ellipse_ang, m.major_axis_b, m.minor_axis_b, m.significance, m.flux_aper_b, m.flux_aper_lolim_b, m.flux_aper_hilim_b, m.ra_aper9#_b, m.dec_aper9#_b, m.mjr_axis_aper9#_b, m.mnr_axis_aper9#_b, m.pos_angle_aper9#_b, m.mjr_axis1_aper9#bkg_b, m.mjr_axis2_aper9#bkg_b, n.distance, s.ra AS ra_sdss, s.dec AS dec_sdss, s.raErr AS raerr_sdss, s.decErr AS decerr_sdss, p.z as photoz, p.zErr as photozerr, s.petroMag_u, s.petroMagErr_u, s.petroMag_g, s.petroMagErr_g, s.petroMag_r, s.petroMagErr_r, s.petroMag_i, s.petroMagErr_i, s.petroMag_z, s.petroMagErr_z, s.petroRad_u, s.petroRadErr_u, s.petroRad_g, s.petroRadErr_g, s.petroRad_r, s.petroRadErr_r, s.petroRad_i, s.petroRadErr_i, s.petroRad_z, s.petroRadErr_z, s.run, s.rerun, s.camcol, s.field, s.obj, (s.flags & dbo.fPhotoFlags (#) ) as NOPETRO, s.nMgyPerCount_u, s.nMgyPerCount_g, s.nMgyPerCount_r, s.nMgyPerCount_i, s.nMgyPerCount_z, h.z as specz, h.zerr as speczerr, h.class, h.subClass, p.kcorrU, p.kcorrG, p.kcorrR, p.kcorrI, p.kcorrZ, gse.bptclass as bptclass, fi.ra as FIRST_ra, fi.dec as FIRST_dec, fi.warning as FIRST_warning, fi.peak as FIRST_peak, fi.integr as FIRST_integr, fi.rms as FIRST_rms, fi.major as FIRST_major, fi.minor as FIRST_minor, fi.pa as FIRST_pa, fi.skyrms as FIRST_skyrms FROM MyDB.CSCv2_v6 AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #/#.) AS n JOIN PhotoObj AS s ON n.objid = s.objid JOIN Photoz AS p ON n.objid = p.objid LEFT JOIN PhotoObjDR7 AS d ON n.objid = d.dr8objid LEFT JOIN SpecObj as h ON s.specObjID = h.specObjID LEFT JOIN galSpecExtra as gse on s.specObjID = gse.specObjID LEFT JOIN FIRST as fi ON fi.objID = n.objid INTO MyDB.CSCv2_v6_SDSSDR1#Photoz_linkDR7_flags_nm_Specz_lines_FIRST
